Cell.Text: Simple... I'm going to cause a distraction and you're going to steal Madesi's silver ring from a strongbox under her stand. | Once you have it, I want you to place it in Brand-Shei's pocket without him noticing.

G|You're trying my patience, lass.

Passing on a golden opportunity is worse.
